Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:59.78,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've stopped caring about the changing of the seasons.{I ceased to care}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.42,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Shirasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:12.92,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Shirasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.50,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Last stop, Wakase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:21.01,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Please wait for the express train, it will come after...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:31.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,How much meaning is there to the fact that it is spring right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.46,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,There's someone else I've fallen in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.82,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Tsubana. Tsubana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:48.54,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Please wait until the train comes to a complete stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, student!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I'm so out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I have about the next arranged marriage party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any particular questions, then I would like to end the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This party is restricted to members in their late 20's to early 30's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, someday I hope to bring down the membership age to include teens,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have a party restricted to women in their teens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't a new restaurant open up in Kanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sorting the membership data files in the back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That face... that smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't show that to customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should definitely be a demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From experience, men my age can only meet teenage girls in an unlawful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's "your" demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any opportunities to meet a female high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm ho...me...{Or just use "tadaima" if you feel like being extra weeaboo, most people know it by now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't told about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're going to be living with Nanoka starting tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show you Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes I do... I do, but I don't remember her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a freshman in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's 15 years old. She is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone commutes from far away nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can cut her commute time from two hours to one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural that we let her stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you got dumped by your lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't intend on getting back together with mom, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a family member!{Or just "She's family!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.14,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,With my carefree life living with Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.84,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:33.58,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I have a mother and a sister who's 12 years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please introduce her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking?{What the hell are you thinking?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you hiding something so important from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's basically like I don't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents got divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met my mom, who took custody of her, a couple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I haven't seen my sister at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of partner are you interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I came while you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my lunch break anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to get the keys to my place{room} back.{More like place, "Heya" is often used to refer to apartments/etc as well as individual rooms}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be better during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really letting me go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just accepted things so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is all I meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.26,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Then what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the party, we're planning to have three events,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if we could divide the food and have it brought out to match the timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, concerning the audio equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. There are for the place next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.  Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:50.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What do I say to a woman that says she has another man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.05,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a place that kind of hurts for a bachelor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cool about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what she dislikes about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try inviting that girl you broke up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you guys will get back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's going to get back together with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm glad. {Or maybe "Thank goodness"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asking out high school girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm interrupting your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is good. I was waiting to meet a someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I came too early and I needed to kill time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meeting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. What would you like to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be boring with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received it during my junior high graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from the person I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't his second button.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.46,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\a6}In Japan it is traditional upon graduating to give the second button from your school uniform to a girl you like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I liked him since I was a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like he's really handsome or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gathered up all my courage and confessed to him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he's going out with a junior at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the window could open, I could throw it out from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still like him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then don't say that you're going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has someone that he's going out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We go to different{separate} high schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll never even see each other anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you love someone so straightforward and honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got dumped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's really different from your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My feelings totally cooled off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really know if I really loved her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should definitely treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the feelings that you have inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I got rejected, I kept walking with my head down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I didn't notice the flowers blooming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you stopped me back at the train station,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The petals were falling like snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and for a moment I couldn't tell where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:11.07,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,That's the same for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.37,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Where is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:20.22,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,this place that I've always been at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.50,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is being here unforgivable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here too, Koshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since you siblings have gotten together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you two recognize each other right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with the two of you? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we have for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother? {Onii-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little sister.
